&lt;p>所以可以写个dfs或者先预处理出每一层m存一下。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>hdu 4704 Sum (隔板法，指数循环节，费马小定理)</title><link>https://111qqz.com/2016/10/hdu-4704-sum-/</link><pubDate>Wed, 26 Oct 2016 10:42:21 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://111qqz.com/2016/10/hdu-4704-sum-/</guid><description>
