&lt;p>题意：M斐波那契数列F[n]是一种整数数列，它的定义如下：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>F[0] = a
F[1] = b
F[n] = F[n-1] * F[n-2] ( n &amp;gt; 1 )&lt;/p>
&lt;p>现在给出a, b, n，你能求出F[n]的值吗？&lt;/p>
&lt;p>思路：观察发现。。。F[n] = a^(fib(n-1)) * b ^ (fib(n))&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>指数循环节学习笔记</title><link>https://111qqz.com/2016/10/</link><pubDate>Wed, 26 Oct 2016 08:59:48 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://111qqz.com/2016/10/</guid><description>
