&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>这&lt;strong>&lt;strong>m&lt;/strong>&lt;/strong>个数&lt;/strong>**{0,1,2,****…****m-1}**&lt;strong>称为一个完全剩余系，&lt;/strong>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>bestcoder #88 || hdu 5908 Abelian Period(暴力)</title><link>https://111qqz.com/2016/10/hdu-5908/</link><pubDate>Sat, 01 Oct 2016 16:11:33 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://111qqz.com/2016/10/hdu-5908/</guid><description>
